\pard\f0\fs28 Sect. GYPSOPHILA. Perennials. Stems up to 25 cm, usually procumbent or ascending. Leaves linear. Inflorescence usually lax or few-flowered; pedicels mostly at least twice as long as calyx. Calyx campanulate. Capsule globose. Ovules 8-16.
\par 

